items.sentence: I'm the one who wrote the song that Tom sang.
I'm the one who told Tom about your accident.
I'm the one who told Tom about what happened.
I'm the one who taught Tom how to play poker.
I'm the one who helped Tom with his homework.
I'm going to do everything I can to find Tom.
I told Tom not to believe everything he read.

I hate Tom's hat. I also hate his sunglasses.
I don't think Tom will be able come tomorrow.
